  "text": "The Discrepancy theory describes that job satisfaction is a result of a comparison between the perception of the current situation and some standard of comparison [CITATION_1] . Adams equity theory suggests that persons who work in an organization compare themselves with others in an equivalent position to determine if they are being treated fairly.",
